{"tid":2381761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國推出「可樂溝咖啡」專家提醒咖啡因多\b一倍","createTime":"2021-01-26T23:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T01:58:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e275e623d696ca419c7c065a5d0faa11b9da32f4","tid":2381761,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:13:34.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）可口可樂公司在美國推出「可樂咖啡」（Coca-Cola with Coffee），五種口味包括深度烘焙（Dark Blend）、雲呢拿（Vanilla）、焦糖（Caramel），以及兩款無糖可樂咖啡，本周起正式在美國上市。公司介紹指，可樂中加入了巴西咖啡豆，以12盎司罐裝出售。但有專家提醒，新產品的咖啡因是普通可樂兩倍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210127/R4Q3DNJPCNCJJLVYLYQXQF7D64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210127%2FR4Q3DNJPCNCJJLVYLYQXQF7D64%2F&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSvw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=d963e233\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210127%2FR4Q3DNJPCNCJJLVYLYQXQF7D64%2F&h=5208e077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210127/R4Q3DNJPCNCJJLVYLYQXQF7D64/</a>"},{"pid":"e19708ae400dad03f3fbdc7cad9a5a573792b6a7","tid":2381761,"uid":38970,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:16:25.000Z","msg":"兩三個月前係香港已經見到有"},{"pid":"be786e5c80312e7631d97b204ac09db1e87e38a3","tid":2381761,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:17:11.000Z","msg":"咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc39028c06b852ac70876e173e302067f1bc022","tid":2381761,"uid":290393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e19708ae400dad03f3fbdc7cad9a5a573792b6a7","tid":2381761,"uid":38970,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:16:25.000Z","msg":"兩三個月前係香港已經見到有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇落好正"},{"pid":"b96a25c7846193826ed82aedb30158a5bf55b400","tid":238176